parameters:
\N<Boku>Wow! It's a fish!... If only I had a
fishing rod, I could catch it...
\N<Boku>Wow! A human soul?! Let's run, Nana- chan!

In that moment, I grabbed her hand in a frenzy and
tried to leave that place.

\N<Nana-chan>Hey, calm down. Wait, it's not a
human soul, it's fireflies.

\N<Boku>So this is a firefly... I've never seen
one before...

\N<Nana-chan>Hey, um... how long are you going to
keep holding my hand?

The expression on her face, illuminated by the
faint light of the fireflies, was not clear, but I
still vividly remember the warmth of her hand from
that moment...
